      <div class="hero__content">
        <p class="hero__label">The Happy Class <span aria-hidden="true">·</span> for Couples</p>
        <h1>Making something <span class="script script--rose">good</span><br />even <span class="hero__underline">better<svg viewBox="0 0 200 14" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2,9 C40,2 90,12 130,6 C160,2 180,8 198,5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>.</h1>
        <p class="hero__sub">A DIY alternative to couples counseling. Not because something's broken - because you want to keep it great.</p>
        <div class="hero__cta-row">
          <a href="#waitlist" class="btn btn--primary btn--large">Join the Waitlist</a>
          <p class="hero__launch">Launching <strong>October 2026</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__visual">
        <img src="/images/hero.png" alt="A warm sunlit table with pink and blue cards, coffee mugs, and a pencil." />
        <span class="confetti confetti--blush"  style="width:24px;height:24px;top:-12px;left:8%;"></span>
        <span class="confetti confetti--butter" style="width:16px;height:16px;bottom:6%;right:-10px;"></span>
        <span class="confetti confetti--sky"    style="width:20px;height:20px;bottom:-8px;left:24%;"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ THE PROBLEM ═══ -->
  <section class="section bg-cream" id="what">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <p class="overline">Here's the thing</p>
      <h2>Most couples don't need therapy.<br />They need <span class="script script--sky">better structure.</span></h2>
      <p class="mx-auto lead">You're not in crisis. You're not falling apart. You love each other. But somewhere along the way, the conversations got shorter, the check-ins stopped, and "we're fine" became the answer to everything. You're good. But you know you could be better.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WHAT IT IS ═══ -->
