          <div class="card__media">
            <img src="/images/vignette-couch.png" alt="Couple on a couch, laughing, holding pink and blue cards." />
          </div>
          <h3>You're solid</h3>
          <p>You're not in trouble. You're not looking for a lifeline. You just know that good relationships don't maintain themselves - they need attention.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__media">
            <img src="/images/vignette-coffee.png" alt="Couple at a cafe table, reading their cards in warm morning light." />
          </div>
          <h3>You want to talk</h3>
          <p>Not about logistics. Not about the kids' schedule. You want the real stuff - the stuff that gets buried under busy. You just need a way in.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__media">
            <img src="/images/vignette-walk.png" alt="Couple walking together on a tree-lined path." />
          </div>
          <h3>Therapy feels like too much</h3>
          <p>You don't need a therapist. You don't need a crisis. You just need a framework that makes it easy to check in with each other - on your own terms, in your own home.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
