        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">01</span>
          <div class="step__media">
            <img src="/images/paper-pink.png" alt="A blush-pink paper card on cream linen." />
          </div>
          <h3>Pick up the <span class="script script--rose">pink</span> paper.</h3>
          <p>Write about your partner. What you see. What you appreciate. What you wish they knew.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">02</span>
          <div class="step__media">
            <img src="/images/paper-blue.png" alt="A sky-blue paper card on cream linen." />
          </div>
          <h3>Pick up the <span class="script script--sky">blue</span> paper.</h3>
          <p>Write about yourself. What you need. What you're carrying. What you haven't said out loud yet.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">03</span>
          <div class="step__media">
            <img src="/images/paper-both.png" alt="Pink and blue paper cards overlapping on linen." />
          </div>
