  <!-- ═══ THE VISION ═══ -->
  <section class="section bg-cream">
    <div class="container container--narrow text-center">
      <div class="sandra-portrait">
        <img src="/images/sandra-portrait.png" alt="Watercolor portrait of Sandra Weise." />
        <span class="confetti confetti--blush"  style="width:18px;height:18px;top:-4px;right:-10px;"></span>
        <span class="confetti confetti--sky"    style="width:14px;height:14px;bottom:4px;left:-14px;"></span>
        <span class="confetti confetti--butter" style="width:12px;height:12px;top:30%;right:-18px;"></span>
      </div>
      <p class="overline">The story behind it</p>
      <h2>Twenty years of sitting across from people in the moments that <span class="script script--sky">matter most.</span></h2>
      <p class="mx-auto" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">I'm Sandra Weise. I've been a life coach for over two decades. I've sat with thousands of people - couples, families, individuals - at the exact moment they realize something needs to change.</p>
      <p class="mx-auto">Here's what I've learned: most couples who walk into a coaching session aren't broken. They're just out of practice. They stopped checking in. They stopped asking each other the real questions. And over time, "fine" replaced "great."</p>
      <p class="mx-auto">The Happy Class is everything I've learned about what makes relationships work - distilled into something you can do at home, together, without a coach in the room. Because you don't need me. You need each other. And a better structure.</p>
      <p class="mx-auto" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><a href="https://sandraweise.com" class="text-link">More about Sandra &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ SOCIAL PROOF ═══ -->
