    <span class="confetti confetti--sky"    style="width:14px;height:14px;top:70%;right:14%;opacity:0.35;"></span>
    <span class="confetti confetti--butter" style="width:12px;height:12px;top:28%;right:22%;opacity:0.3;"></span>
    <div class="container container--narrow text-center">
      <h2 style="color: var(--linen);">Be the <span class="script script--butter">first</span> to know.</h2>
      <p style="color: rgba(250,246,240,0.7); margin: 1rem auto 2.5rem; max-width: 480px;">The Happy Class for Couples launches October 2026. Drop your email and we'll let you know the moment it's ready.</p>

